{"tid":1631811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣一招，用朱溶基段片反分化中共","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:46.000Z","uid":306208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf2f902da5100a473cb15f53fc2070f3527bffd","tid":1631811,"uid":306208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"文宣一招，用朱溶基段片分化中共<br />\n<br />\n攪亂香港，係中共既錯<br />\n<br />\n江派人會用呢樣野反習近平<br />\n<br />\n我們反分化中共，我們才有機天滅中共"},{"pid":"8e300e9d2ebfa53772dde8eba45657ec5405fba0","tid":1631811,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文宣國際線要你幫手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d16d184cfc05e2007184663c375a3aa5458c516","tid":1631811,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"15488440cbf505b7f6917b37dff5f3e099f1de17","tid":1631811,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06a5d4dddc23e307996b331cc90118561d0441c","tid":1631811,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"咩片"},{"pid":"4fde7e0c450819dc313170476ab7a5a686810a28","tid":1631811,"uid":306208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06a5d4dddc23e307996b331cc90118561d0441c","tid":1631811,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"咩片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100006656760358/videos/2528600200705181?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100006656760358%2Fvideos%2F2528600200705181%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=4845396e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100006656760358/videos/2528600200705181?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n佢話香港攪不好就係中共既責任，中共係千古罪人"},{"pid":"90933947ea93a8e38bd57bbf633ef2afff9bf073","tid":1631811,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fde7e0c450819dc313170476ab7a5a686810a28","tid":1631811,"uid":306208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06a5d4dddc2